headline: CMS Energy's Board of Directors Declares Quarterly Dividend on Common Stock
summary: The Board of Directors of CMS Energy has declared a quarterly dividend on the company's common stock.

headline: Energy Savings Programs Help Customers Use Energy Wisely, Support Grid Reliability
summary: Consumers Energy is reaffirming its commitment to helping customers use energy more wisely through various energy savings programs that not only lower bills but also support the long-term reliability of the electric grid. Since the launch of energy waste reduction programs in 2009 through 2024, energy savings from both gas and electric initiatives have totaled the annual output of 18 natural gas power plants.
